title: I'm Alan Partridge - series 2
description:
Series 2 was made in 2002 and finds Alan trying to regain his B list celebrity status since he has bounced back and got the third best slot on the radio. 

He has left the Linton Travel Tavern and is living in a static caravan, with a Ukrainian girlfriend 14 years his junior, whilst his suburban mansion is being constructed.

Some classics include an encounter with a sex mad couple, injuring himself on a guard rail and the James Bondathon.

Review of the series on imd at http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0129690/ gives a rating of 9.3/10.

Six half hour episodes in divx format.
